When i was 15, I liked English so much, i wish i could study aboard in countries like Paris, Paris...So i decided to take the professional English class in highschool. It was like an exam. But, there are so many peoples, students who wanna take themselfs in this class too. And then, i failed this exam
But luckily, i got enough marks to take a professional French in highschool. I was so confused because i have never learn French before, I haved to start at 0. A year later, i know that i can speak French, i can understand and think in French. So i decided to study  aboard in Paris.
The problem that i want to study aboard but in what field? I don't like the jobs in office for 8 hours, it's so boring. But i can't be an actor or singer. I have no ideal. When i was wondering, my teacher talked about the media industry, which is a dynamic industry, without numbers and i can do many differents jobs. So i have explored this field for a long time an i have chosen this major to study aboard, in Paris.
And after i graduate, i want to be an event oganizer.
 This webpage performs keylogging of input typed into a textbox. In other words, when focused on the textbox below, the page will record each time you hit a key or select text with your mouse. All of the data is stored locally on your machine in the DOM and is downloadable as a JSON file.
